authSocket PACKAGE

Package authSocket la noi chua 2 Class Component quan trong de cau hinh xac dinh danh tinh nguoi dung va quan ly
phien ket noi tu nguoi dung mot cach chu dong. Trong do:

    1. WsAuthInterceptor Component
       Day la Class Component xac dinh danh tinh nguoi dung truy cap web socket thong qua token tu nguoi dung
       cu the.

       Class Component nay duoc khoi tao boi vi ung dung Spring Frontend tai thu muc admin [FE_Admin] dong vai tro
       la mot Proxy BFF (Backend For Frontend) khong quan ly truc tiep nguoi dung bang HttpSession nhu server goc,
       nen khi mot nguoi dung ket noi vao socket thi BFF hoan toan khong the tu nhan biet duoc danh tinh tu nguoi dung
       do. Class Component WsAuthInterceptor se giup BFF thuc hien duoc dieu nay khi nguoi dung login thanh cong va
       token la du lieu can thiet de xac thuc nguoi dung do.

       Co the review Logic tai "admin/src/main/resources/static/assets/js/app/main.js", Day la file render chinh cho
       ung dung SPA va cau hinh ket noi Web Socket tu SPA.

    2. WebSocketEvenListener Component
       Day la Class Component quan ly phien ket noi Socket cho ca 2 trang thai Connect va Disconnect ma khong phu
       thuoc vao hanh dong truc tiep tu nguoi dung.

       Voi trang thai Login thanh cong, socket tu nhan biet nguoi dung ket noi socket

       Voi trang thai Disconnect (token het han tu thoat phien va nguoi dung thuc hien logout), socket tu nhan
       biet va gui thong bao thong qua luong Downstream cua Socket den UI da Subscribe thong bao


Nhu vay, Trong truong hop ung dung admin Spring Frontend cua toi dong vai tro la mot BFF thi day la 2 Class Component
quan trong khi su dung dich vu Web Socket ma hoan toan khong phu thuoc vao BE goc cua toan bo du an => server [dabble]

2 Class Component nay ap dung cho nguoi dung truy cap truc tiep tren ung dung admin BFF, doi voi nguoi dung truy cap
tu mot ung dung khac thi WebsocketController la noi ghi nhan du lieu
